title: Dental Plans
description: Dental Plans brand features a distinct palette showcasing professionalism and vibrancy with colors like neutral grey (#F2F2F4), energetic blue (#2445EA), soothing pink (#BC578E), calming green (#77C79B), vibrant orange (#EA5B38), sunny yellow (#E89E34), and bold black (#070808). Information about these colors can be found in their comprehensive brand guidelines from 2019.
